#: mod/lostpass.php:28
msgid "No valid account found."
msgstr "找不到有效帳戶。"

#: mod/lostpass.php:40
msgid "Password reset request issued. Check your email."
msgstr "已發出密碼重置請求。檢視你的郵件。\n "

#: mod/lostpass.php:46
#, php-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"\t\tDear %1$s,\n"
"\t\t\tA request was recently received at \"%2$s\" to reset your account\n"
"\t\tpassword. In order to confirm this request, please select the verification link\n"
"\t\tbelow or paste it into your web browser address bar.\n"
"\n"
"\t\tIf you did NOT request this change, please DO NOT follow the link\n"
"\t\tprovided and ignore and/or delete this email, the request will expire shortly.\n"
"\n"
"\t\tYour password will not be changed unless we can verify that you\n"
"\t\tissued this request."
msgstr "\n\t\t親愛的%1$s，\n\t\t\t“%2$s收到重置帳號密碼的請求。\n\t\t為了確認此請求，請選擇驗證連結\n\t\t忽視或將其貼上到您的網頁瀏覽器位址列中。\n\n\t\t如果您沒有請求更改密碼，無須任何操作\n\t\t忽視並/或刪除此電子郵件，此請求會很快過期。\n\n\t\t除非我們可以驗證此請求是您發出的，\n\t\t您的密碼將不會被更改。"

#: mod/lostpass.php:57
#, php-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"\t\tFollow this link soon to verify your identity:\n"
"\n"
"\t\t%1$s\n"
"\n"
"\t\tYou will then receive a follow-up message containing the new password.\n"
"\t\tYou may change that password from your account settings page after logging in.\n"
"\n"
"\t\tThe login details are as follows:\n"
"\n"
"\t\tSite Location:\t%2$s\n"
"\t\tLogin Name:\t%3$s"
msgstr "\n\t\t請點選此連結並驗證您的身份：\n\n\t\t%1$s\n\n\t\t後續您會收到含有新的密碼的訊息。\n\t\t登入後，您可以在您的帳號設定頁面更改密碼。\n\n\t\t登入詳情如下：\n\n\t\t站點位置：\t%2$s\n\t\t登入名稱：\t%3$s"

#: mod/lostpass.php:72
#, php-format
msgid "Password reset requested at %s"
msgstr "密碼重置請求於%s"

#: mod/lostpass.php:88
msgid ""
"Request could not be verified. (You may have previously submitted it.) "
"Password reset failed."
msgstr "無法驗證請求。 （您之前可能已經提交過。）密碼重置失敗。"

#: mod/lostpass.php:101
msgid "Request has expired, please make a new one."
msgstr "請求超時，請重試。"

#: mod/lostpass.php:116
msgid "Forgot your Password?"
msgstr "忘記你的密碼了？"

#: mod/lostpass.php:117
msgid ""
"Enter your email address and submit to have your password reset. Then check "
"your email for further instructions."
msgstr "輸入您的電子郵件地址並提交以重置密碼。然後檢視您的電子郵件以獲取接下來的步驟。"

#: mod/lostpass.php:118 src/Module/Security/Login.php:167
msgid "Nickname or email"
msgstr ""

#: mod/lostpass.php:119
msgid "Reset my password"
msgstr ""

#: mod/lostpass.php:134 src/Module/Security/Login.php:179
msgid "Password Reset"
msgstr "密碼重置"

#: mod/lostpass.php:135
msgid "Your password has been reset as requested."
msgstr "您的密碼已被重設。"

#: mod/lostpass.php:136
msgid "Your new password is"
msgstr "您的新密碼是"

#: mod/lostpass.php:137
msgid "Save or copy your new password - and then"
msgstr "儲存或複製您的新密碼——然後"

#: mod/lostpass.php:138
msgid "click here to login"
msgstr "點選這裡登入"

#: mod/lostpass.php:139
msgid ""
"Your password may be changed from the <em>Settings</em> page after "
"successful login."
msgstr "您的密碼可以在成功登入後在<em>設定</em>頁修改。"

#: mod/lostpass.php:143
msgid "Your password has been reset."
msgstr "您的密碼已被重置。"

#: mod/lostpass.php:146
#, php-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"\t\t\tDear %1$s,\n"
"\t\t\t\tYour password has been changed as requested. Please retain this\n"
"\t\t\tinformation for your records (or change your password immediately to\n"
"\t\t\tsomething that you will remember).\n"
"\t\t"
msgstr "\n\t\t\t親愛的%1$s：\n\t\t\t\t您的密碼已按您的要求更改了。請保留\n\t\t\t此訊息作為記錄（或立即將您的密碼更改為\n\t\t\t一些你會記住的東西）。\n\t\t"

#: mod/lostpass.php:152
#, php-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"\t\t\tYour login details are as follows:\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\tSite Location:\t%1$s\n"
"\t\t\tLogin Name:\t%2$s\n"
"\t\t\tPassword:\t%3$s\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\tYou may change that password from your account settings page after logging in.\n"
"\t\t"
msgstr "\n\t\t\t您的登入詳細資訊如下：\n\n\t\t\t站點位置：\t%1$s\n\t\t\t登入名：\t%2$s\n\t\t\t密碼：\t%3$s\n\n\t\t\t您可以在登入後從帳號設定頁面更改該密碼。\n\t\t"

