msgid ""
"With checking this, every user is allowed to mark every contact as a "
"remote_self in the repair contact dialog. Setting this flag on a contact "
"causes mirroring every posting of that contact in the users stream."
msgstr "選擇這個之後，使用者們允許表明熟人當遙遠的自身在熟人修理頁。遙遠的自身所有文章被複制到使用者文章流。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:527
msgid "Allow Users to set up relay channels"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:527
msgid ""
"If enabled, it is possible to create relay users that are used to reshare "
"content based on user defined channels."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:528
msgid "Adjust the feed poll frequency"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:528
msgid "Automatically detect and set the best feed poll frequency."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:529
msgid "Minimum poll interval"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:529
msgid ""
"Minimal distance in minutes between two polls for mail and feed contacts. "
"Reasonable values are between 1 and 59."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:530
msgid "Enable multiple registrations"
msgstr "啟用多人註冊"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:530
msgid "Enable users to register additional accounts for use as pages."
msgstr "允許使用者註冊其他帳戶型別以用作頁面。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:531
msgid "Enable OpenID"
msgstr "啟用OpenID"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:531
msgid "Enable OpenID support for registration and logins."
msgstr "為註冊和登入啟用 OpenID 支援。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:532
msgid "Enable full name check"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:532
msgid ""
"Prevents users from registering with a display name with fewer than two "
"parts separated by spaces."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:533
msgid "Email administrators on new registration"
msgstr "新註冊的電子郵件管理員"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:533
msgid ""
"If enabled and the system is set to an open registration, an email for each "
"new registration is sent to the administrators."
msgstr "如果啟用開放註冊，則每次新註冊都會向管理員傳送一封電子郵件。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:534
msgid "Community pages for visitors"
msgstr "訪問者的社群頁面"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:534
msgid ""
"Which community pages should be available for visitors. Local users always "
"see both pages."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:535
msgid "Posts per user on community page"
msgstr "個使用者文章數量在社會頁"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:535
msgid ""
"The maximum number of posts per user on the local community page. This is "
"useful, when a single user floods the local community page."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:536
msgid "Posts per server on community page"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:536
msgid ""
"The maximum number of posts per server on the global community page. This is"
" useful, when posts from a single server flood the global community page."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:537
msgid "Display local media to visitors"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:537
msgid ""
"When enabled, locally stored media, such as pictures and videos, will be "
"displayed to visitors who are not logged in. When disabled, a message will "
"appear informing visitors that the media is only available to logged-in "
"users."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:538
msgid "Display remote media to visitors"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:538
msgid ""
"When enabled, visitors who are not logged in will be able to view non-"
"locally stored media such as pictures and videos. When disabled, visitors "
"will see a message informing them that the media is available on the remote "
"site."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:540
msgid "Enable Mail support"
msgstr "啟用郵件支援"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:540
msgid ""
"Enable built-in mail support to poll IMAP folders and to reply via mail."
msgstr "啟用內建郵件支援以查詢 IMAP 資料夾並透過郵件回覆。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:541
msgid ""
"Mail support can't be enabled because the PHP IMAP module is not installed."
msgstr "無法啟用郵件支援，因為未安裝 PHP IMAP 模組。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:543
msgid ""
"Diaspora support can't be enabled because Friendica was installed into a sub"
" directory."
msgstr "Diaspora 支援無法啟用，因為 Friendica 被安裝到了一個子目錄。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:544
msgid "Enable Diaspora support"
msgstr "啟用 Diaspora 支援"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:544
msgid ""
"Enable built-in Diaspora network compatibility for communicating with "
"diaspora servers."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:545
msgid "Verify SSL"
msgstr "驗證 SSL"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:545
msgid ""
"If you wish, you can turn on strict certificate checking. This will mean you"
" cannot connect (at all) to self-signed SSL sites."
msgstr "如果您願意，可以嚴格的證書檢查。這意味著您無法連線到自簽名 SSL 站點。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:546
msgid "Proxy user"
msgstr "代理使用者"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:546
msgid "User name for the proxy server."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:547
msgid "Proxy URL"
msgstr "代理URL"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:547
msgid ""
"If you want to use a proxy server that Friendica should use to connect to "
"the network, put the URL of the proxy here."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:548
msgid "Network timeout"
msgstr "網路超時"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:548
msgid "Value is in seconds. Set to 0 for unlimited (not recommended)."
msgstr "輸入秒數。輸入零為無限（不推薦的）。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:549
msgid "Maximum Load Average"
msgstr "最大平均負荷"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:549
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Maximum system load before delivery and poll processes are deferred - "
"default %d."
msgstr "延遲傳遞和輪詢過程之前的最大系統負載-預設值%d。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:550
msgid "Minimal Memory"
msgstr "最少記憶體"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:550
msgid ""
"Minimal free memory in MB for the worker. Needs access to /proc/meminfo - "
"default 0 (deactivated)."
msgstr "後臺程序的最小可用記憶體（以 MB 為單位）。需要訪問 /proc/meminfo - 預設 0（停用）。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:551
msgid "Periodically optimize tables"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:551
msgid "Periodically optimize tables like the cache and the workerqueue"
msgstr "定期最佳化快取和 workerqueue 等表"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:553
msgid "Discover followers/followings from contacts"
msgstr "從聯絡人中發現關注者/粉絲"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:553
msgid ""
"If enabled, contacts are checked for their followers and following contacts."
msgstr "如果啟用，則會重新檢查聯絡人的關注和關注者。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:554
msgid "None - deactivated"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:555
msgid ""
"Local contacts - contacts of our local contacts are discovered for their "
"followers/followings."
msgstr "本站好友 - 讓他們的好友發現本站的成員的聯絡人。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:556
msgid ""
"Interactors - contacts of our local contacts and contacts who interacted on "
"locally visible postings are discovered for their followers/followings."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:558
msgid "Only update contacts/servers with local data"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:558
msgid ""
"If enabled, the system will only look for changes in contacts and servers "
"that engaged on this system by either being in a contact list of a user or "
"when posts or comments exists from the contact on this system."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:559
msgid "Only update contacts with relations"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:559
msgid ""
"If enabled, the system will only look for changes in contacts that are in a "
"contact list of a user on this system."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:560
msgid "Synchronize the contacts with the directory server"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:560
msgid ""
"if enabled, the system will check periodically for new contacts on the "
"defined directory server."
msgstr "如果啟用，系統將定期檢查目錄伺服器上是否有新的聯絡人。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:562
msgid "Discover contacts from other servers"
msgstr "從其他伺服器上發現聯絡人"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:562
msgid ""
"Periodically query other servers for contacts and servers that they know of."
" The system queries Friendica, Mastodon and Hubzilla servers. Keep it "
"deactivated on small machines to decrease the database size and load."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:563
msgid "Days between requery"
msgstr "重新查詢間隔天數"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:563
msgid ""
"Number of days after which a server is requeried for their contacts and "
"servers it knows of. This is only used when the discovery is activated."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:564
msgid "Search the local directory"
msgstr "搜尋本地目錄"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:564
msgid ""
"Search the local directory instead of the global directory. When searching "
"locally, every search will be executed on the global directory in the "
"background. This improves the search results when the search is repeated."
msgstr "搜尋本地目錄，而不是全域性目錄。在本地搜尋時，每次搜尋都將在後臺對全域性目錄執行。這會在重複搜尋時改進搜尋結果。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:566
msgid "Publish server information"
msgstr "釋出伺服器資訊"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:566
msgid ""
"If enabled, general server and usage data will be published. The data "
"contains the name and version of the server, number of users with public "
"profiles, number of posts and the activated protocols and connectors. See <a"
" href=\"http://the-federation.info/\">the-federation.info</a> for details."
msgstr "如果啟用，將釋出常規伺服器和使用資料。這些資料包括伺服器的名稱和版本、擁有公共配置檔案的使用者數量、帖子數量以及啟用的協議和聯結器。有關詳細資訊，請參閱-<a href=\"http://the-federation.info/\">the-federation.info</a>。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:568
msgid "Check upstream version"
msgstr "檢查上游版本"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:568
msgid ""
"Enables checking for new Friendica versions at github. If there is a new "
"version, you will be informed in the admin panel overview."
msgstr "啟用在 github 上檢查新的 Friendica 版本。如果發現新版本，您將在管理員概要面板得到通知。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:569
msgid "Suppress Tags"
msgstr "壓制標籤"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:569
msgid "Suppress showing a list of hashtags at the end of the posting."
msgstr "不在文章末尾顯示主題標籤列表。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:570
msgid "Clean database"
msgstr "清理資料庫"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:570
msgid ""
"Remove old remote items, orphaned database records and old content from some"
" other helper tables."
msgstr "從一些其他幫助器表中刪除舊的遠端專案、孤立的資料庫記錄和舊內容。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:571
msgid "Lifespan of remote items"
msgstr "遠端專案的使用期限"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:571
msgid ""
"When the database cleanup is enabled, this defines the days after which "
"remote items will be deleted. Own items, and marked or filed items are "
"always kept. 0 disables this behaviour."
msgstr "啟用資料庫清理後，這將定義刪除遠端專案的天數。自己的物品，標記或歸檔的物品總是儲存著。0禁用此行為。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:572
msgid "Lifespan of unclaimed items"
msgstr "與本站從未互動的內容"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:572
msgid ""
"When the database cleanup is enabled, this defines the days after which "
"unclaimed remote items (mostly content from the relay) will be deleted. "
"Default value is 90 days. Defaults to the general lifespan value of remote "
"items if set to 0."
msgstr "當啟用資料庫清理，來自遠端例項的快取（主要是來自中繼的內容）將被刪。預設值為 90 天。如果設定為 0，預設為遠端內容的一般壽命值。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:573
msgid "Lifespan of raw conversation data"
msgstr "帖子或評論的生命週期"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:573
msgid ""
"The conversation data is used for ActivityPub, as well as for debug "
"purposes. It should be safe to remove it after 14 days, default is 90 days."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:574
msgid "Maximum numbers of comments per post"
msgstr "檔案最多評論"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:574
msgid "How much comments should be shown for each post? Default value is 100."
msgstr "每個帖子顯示多少評論？預設100."

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:575
msgid "Maximum numbers of comments per post on the display page"
msgstr "顯示帖子的最大評論數"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:575
msgid ""
"How many comments should be shown on the single view for each post? Default "
"value is 1000."
msgstr "每個帖子評論區顯示多少條評論？ 預設值為 1000。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:576
msgid "Items per page"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:576
msgid ""
"Number of items per page in stream pages (network, community, "
"profile/contact statuses, search)."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:577
msgid "Items per page for mobile devices"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:577
msgid ""
"Number of items per page in stream pages (network, community, "
"profile/contact statuses, search) for mobile devices."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:578
msgid "Temp path"
msgstr "臨時檔案路線"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:578
msgid ""
"If you have a restricted system where the webserver can't access the system "
"temp path, enter another path here."
msgstr "如果您有受限制的系統，其中Web伺服器無法訪問系統臨時路徑，請在此處輸入其他路徑。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:579
msgid "Only search in tags"
msgstr "只在標籤項內搜尋"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:579
msgid "On large systems the text search can slow down the system extremely."
msgstr "在大型系統中，正文搜尋會極大降低系統執行速度。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:580
msgid "Limited search scope"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:580
msgid ""
"If enabled, searches will only be performed in the data used for the "
"channels and not in all posts."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:581
msgid "Maximum age of items in the search table"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:581
msgid ""
"Maximum age of items in the search table in days. Lower values will increase"
" the performance and reduce disk usage. 0 means no age restriction."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:582
msgid "Generate counts per contact circle when calculating network count"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:582
msgid ""
"On systems with users that heavily use contact circles the query can be very"
" expensive."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:583
msgid "Process \"view\" activities"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:583
msgid ""
"\"view\" activities are mostly geberated by Peertube systems. Per default "
"they are not processed for performance reasons. Only activate this option on"
" performant system."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:584
msgid "Days, after which a contact is archived"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:584
msgid ""
"Number of days that we try to deliver content or to update the contact data "
"before we archive a contact."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:586
msgid "Maximum number of parallel workers"
msgstr "併發最大數量"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:586
#, php-format
msgid ""
"On shared hosters set this to %d. On larger systems, values of %d are great."
" Default value is %d."
msgstr "在共享主機上設定為 %d。在較大的系統上應設定為%d。預設值為%d。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:587
msgid "Maximum load for workers"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:587
msgid "Maximum load that causes a cooldown before each worker function call."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:588
msgid "Enable fastlane"
msgstr "啟用快車道模式"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:588
msgid ""
"When enabed, the fastlane mechanism starts an additional worker if processes"
" with higher priority are blocked by processes of lower priority."
msgstr "啟用後，如果優先順序較高的程序被阻塞，fastlane 機制會啟動一個額外的 worker程序。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:589
msgid "Decoupled receiver"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:589
msgid ""
"Decouple incoming ActivityPub posts by processing them in the background via"
" a worker process. Only enable this on fast systems."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:590
msgid "Fetch replies mode"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:590
msgid "Missing replies can be fetched upon receipt of an ActivityPub post."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:591
msgid "Cron interval"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:591
msgid "Minimal period in minutes between two calls of the \"Cron\" worker job."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:592
msgid "Worker defer limit"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:592
msgid ""
"Per default the systems tries delivering for 15 times before dropping it."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:593
msgid "Worker fetch limit"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:593
msgid ""
"Number of worker tasks that are fetched in a single query. Higher values "
"should increase the performance, too high values will mostly likely decrease"
" it. Only change it, when you know how to measure the performance of your "
"system."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:595
msgid "Direct relay transfer"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:595
msgid ""
"Enables the direct transfer to other servers without using the relay servers"
msgstr "無需使用中繼站即可直接傳輸到其他例項"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:596
msgid "Relay scope"
msgstr "中繼範圍"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:596
msgid ""
"Can be \"all\" or \"tags\". \"all\" means that every public post should be "
"received. \"tags\" means that only posts with selected tags should be "
"received."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:596 src/Module/Contact/Profile.php:354
#: src/Module/Settings/Display.php:269
#: src/Module/Settings/TwoFactor/Index.php:132
msgid "Disabled"
msgstr "已停用"

