msgstr "Friendica歡迎你"

#: src/Module/Welcome.php:32
msgid "New Member Checklist"
msgstr "新成員清單"

#: src/Module/Welcome.php:33
msgid ""
"We would like to offer some tips and links to help make your experience "
"enjoyable. Click any item to visit the relevant page. A link to this page "
"will be visible from your home page for two weeks after your initial "
"registration and then will quietly disappear."
msgstr "我們想提供一些建議和連結以助於讓你有愉快的經歷。點選任意一項訪問相應的網頁。在你註冊之後，到這個頁面的連結會在你的主頁顯示兩週，之後悄聲地消失。"

#: src/Module/Welcome.php:35
msgid "Getting Started"
msgstr "入門"

#: src/Module/Welcome.php:36
msgid "Friendica Walk-Through"
msgstr "Friendica 漫遊"

#: src/Module/Welcome.php:37
msgid ""
"Complete the walk-through to get a quick overview of your profile and "
"network tabs, establish new connections and find groups to join."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Welcome.php:40
msgid "Go to Your Settings"
msgstr "您的設定"

#: src/Module/Welcome.php:41
msgid ""
"On your <em>Settings</em> page -  change your initial password. Also make a "
"note of your Identity Address. This looks just like an email address - and "
"will be useful in making friends on the free social web."
msgstr "在你的<em>設定</em>頁 - 改變你最初的密碼。同時也記住你的身份地址。這看起來像一個電子郵件地址 - 並且在這個自由的社交網路交友時會有用。"

#: src/Module/Welcome.php:42
msgid ""
"Review the other settings, particularly the privacy settings. An unpublished"
" directory listing is like having an unlisted phone number. In general, you "
"should probably publish your listing - unless all of your friends and "
"potential friends know exactly how to find you."
msgstr "校對別的設定，特別是隱私設定。一個未釋出的目錄專案是跟未出版的電話號碼一樣。平時，你可能應該出版你的目錄專案-除非都你的朋友們和可交的朋友們已經知道確切地怎麼找你。"

#: src/Module/Welcome.php:45
msgid "Upload Profile Photo"
msgstr "上傳頭像"

#: src/Module/Welcome.php:46
msgid ""
"Upload a profile photo if you have not done so already. Studies have shown "
"that people with real photos of themselves are ten times more likely to make"
" friends than people who do not."
msgstr "上傳一張簡歷照片除非你已經做過。研究表明有真正自己的照片的人比沒有的交朋友們可能多十倍。"

#: src/Module/Welcome.php:47
msgid "Edit Your Profile"
msgstr "編輯您的簡介"

#: src/Module/Welcome.php:48
msgid ""
"Edit your <strong>default</strong> profile to your liking. Review the "
"settings for hiding your list of friends and hiding the profile from unknown"
" visitors."
msgstr "根據您的喜好編輯您的 <strong>預設</strong>個人資料。檢視隱藏好友列表和對未知訪問者隱藏個人資料的設定。"

#: src/Module/Welcome.php:49
msgid "Profile Keywords"
msgstr "簡介關鍵字"

#: src/Module/Welcome.php:50
msgid ""
"Set some public keywords for your profile which describe your interests. We "
"may be able to find other people with similar interests and suggest "
"friendships."
msgstr "為你的個人資料設定一些描述你興趣的公共關鍵字。我們也許能找到其他有相似興趣的人，並建議結交朋友。"

#: src/Module/Welcome.php:52
msgid "Connecting"
msgstr "連線著"

#: src/Module/Welcome.php:54
msgid "Importing Emails"
msgstr "正在匯入郵件"

#: src/Module/Welcome.php:55
msgid ""
"Enter your email access information on your Connector Settings page if you "
"wish to import and interact with friends or mailing lists from your email "
"INBOX"
msgstr "如果您希望從您的電子郵件收件箱匯入朋友或郵寄列表並與之互動，請在您的聯結器設定頁面上輸入您的電子郵件訪問資訊"

#: src/Module/Welcome.php:56
msgid "Go to Your Contacts Page"
msgstr "轉到您的聯絡人頁面"

#: src/Module/Welcome.php:57
msgid ""
"Your Contacts page is your gateway to managing friendships and connecting "
"with friends on other networks. Typically you enter their address or site "
"URL in the <em>Add New Contact</em> dialog."
msgstr "您熟人頁是您門口為管理熟人和連線朋友們在別的網路。典型您輸入他的地址或者網站URL在<em>新增新熟人</em>對話方塊。"

#: src/Module/Welcome.php:58
msgid "Go to Your Site's Directory"
msgstr "您網站的目錄"

#: src/Module/Welcome.php:59
msgid ""
"The Directory page lets you find other people in this network or other "
"federated sites. Look for a <em>Connect</em> or <em>Follow</em> link on "
"their profile page. Provide your own Identity Address if requested."
msgstr "目錄頁讓你在這個網路或者其他的聯邦的站點找到其他人。在他們的簡介頁找一個<em>連線</em>或<em>關注</em>連結。如果需要，提供你自己的身份地址。"

#: src/Module/Welcome.php:60
msgid "Finding New People"
msgstr "找新人"

#: src/Module/Welcome.php:61
msgid ""
"On the side panel of the Contacts page are several tools to find new "
"friends. We can match people by interest, look up people by name or "
"interest, and provide suggestions based on network relationships. On a brand"
" new site, friend suggestions will usually begin to be populated within 24 "
"hours."
msgstr "在“聯絡人”頁面的側面板上有幾個用於尋找新朋友的工具。 我們可以按興趣匹配，按姓名或興趣查詢人，並根據網路關係提供建議。 在一個全新的站點上，推薦好友 通常會在 24 小時內開始填充。"

#: src/Module/Welcome.php:64
msgid "Add Your Contacts To Circle"
msgstr "將您的聯絡人新增到圈子"

#: src/Module/Welcome.php:65
msgid ""
"Once you have made some friends, organize them into private conversation "
"circles from the sidebar of your Contacts page and then you can interact "
"with each circle privately on your Network page."
msgstr "一旦您認識了一些朋友，就可以從“聯絡人”頁面的側邊欄將他們組織到私人對話圈中，然後您可以在“主頁”頁面上與每個圈子私下互動。"

#: src/Module/Welcome.php:67
msgid "Why Aren't My Posts Public?"
msgstr "我文章怎麼沒公開的？"

#: src/Module/Welcome.php:68
msgid ""
"Friendica respects your privacy. By default, your posts will only show up to"
" people you've added as friends. For more information, see the help section "
"from the link above."
msgstr "Friendica尊敬您的隱私。預設是您文章只被您朋友們看。更多訊息在幫助部分在上面的連結。"

#: src/Module/Welcome.php:70
msgid "Getting Help"
msgstr "獲取幫助"

#: src/Module/Welcome.php:71
msgid "Go to the Help Section"
msgstr "看幫助部分"

#: src/Module/Welcome.php:72
msgid ""
"Our <strong>help</strong> pages may be consulted for detail on other program"
" features and resources."
msgstr "我們<strong>幫助</strong>頁可查閱到詳情關於別的程式設計特點和資源。"

